I"ü<p><strong>Infinite ads</strong> is a feature we introduced to our latest release 2.1.4. With this feature activated you can <strong>see ads will be loading automatically</strong> whenever the user scrolls down, without the need to click on a page number or next page.</p>

<p><strong>To activate infinite scroll</strong> follow the next steps:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Go to <strong>Appearance</strong> &gt; <strong>Theme options</strong></li>
  <li>Change <strong>Infinite scroll</strong> to <strong>YES</strong></li>
  <li>Press <strong>Update</strong></li>
</ol>

<p>And it will be working perfectly!</p>

<p>If you have any feedback or suggestion feel free to leave a comment in the section below.</p>

